fields.value: Replication data for: Assessing grafting aptitude of Allanblackia floribunda using three techniques in the nursery

dsDescriptionValue.value: The study was carried out to assess grafting aptitude of Allanblackia floribunda using three techniques in the nursery of Yaounde Cameroon. The treatment for this study were: side T, Whipn T, Side V and Top C with 40 repetitions. Data were recorded after one week of planting for a period of 12 weeks. The result was recorded as dormant, success, dead and the number of leaves if success.
